WHO   — The Formats — Standard · Historic · Alchemy · Limited
WHAT  — The rule-sets that shape the metagame, including Alchemy — cards that exist only digitally and can be rebalanced live, which only a digital game can do.
WHERE — MTG · MTG Arena  Framework inputs: Magic: The Gathering / MTG Arena (WotC)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
